763
01:00:41,110 --> 01:00:42,355
Dam.

764
01:00:44,280 --> 01:00:45,565
Bangun.

765
01:00:49,690 --> 01:00:50,885
Berhenti…

766
01:00:54,050 --> 01:00:55,285
melihatnya.

